name: UniversalVTTImporter
description: Imports UniversalVTT files, `.dd2vtt`, as used by Dungeondraft.See the *Help: UniversalVTTImporter* Handout in game for help, or run `!uvtt --help`, or visit [UniversalVTTImporter Forum Thread](https://app.roll20.net/forum/permalink/8824428/).You can also visit [UniversalVTTImporter Sanitizer](http://roll20api.net/uvtti.html) for instructions and a handy file sanititzer.
